msgctxt "0001"
msgid "What was in your video, Taka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "I saw...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"Sorry... It's gonna take me some time to figure out\n"
"how to put it into words..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid "Everyone's really upset..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid "I mean, how could anyone be calm right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"Why...? How can something like that even exist? I just\n"
"don't understand. I don't..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"To be able to do something like that... Is it because\n"
"they really are the murderous fiend?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"Hey, Makoto! These videos are some kinda hoax, right?\n"
"Right!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid "I want to think so. But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid "Wh-What the hell, man!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "This is all one big lie! It has to be! Hahaha...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid "Urg..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid "What was in your video, Kyoko?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Why should I tell you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid "What was in your video, Sakura?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0018"
msgid "My family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid "But I'm not upset by what I saw."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"If you're overpowered, you must accept your death.\n"
"That is the way of my family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"But still...I refuse to believe they would lose so\n"
"easily. How...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid "What was in your video, Hifumi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "Ngh...grnnngh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid ""
"Before you go asking someone else, it's only polite\n"
"that *you* say what *you* saw first, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "Well, I—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid "...Why are you covering your ears?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"If I don't hear yours, I don't have to say mine! It's\n"
"the art of see no evil, hear no evil, speak no evil!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I don't think that's how it works...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"Hey Makoto, aren't you like super curious what's in\n"
"everyone's videos?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid "I mean...I can't say I'm *not* curious..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Right? I could totally tell!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"But...does that mean you're gonna tell me what was in\n"
"yours?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"Hmm, who knows? It all depends what kinda mood I'm in,\n"
"ya know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I don't think she's gonna tell me...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid "What was in your video, Celeste?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid "Oh, it is you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "You really want to know, don't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Th-That smile... It's strangely scary.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"There are many, many things in this world you are\n"
"better off not knowing, don't you think?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "What was in your video, Mondo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid "H-Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid "Oh, it doesn't matter. It's not a big deal!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"It was fake, anyway. It had to be! Whoever's doing all\n"
"this just pulled it out of his ass!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"Yeah, that's gotta be it! Those assholes can't fool\n"
"me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid "What was in your video, Byakuya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid "...Hmph."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid ""
"Where is it written I have to tell you? You wouldn't\n"
"understand anyway. Now leave me alone. You bore me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid "I'm not sayin' nothin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid ""
"I'm not gonna tell you! No way! Hell no! No way in\n"
"hell!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid ""
"You're just acting all nice so we'll tell you what you\n"
"wanna hear. You can't fool me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid "Dammit! How the hell did they get footage of that...!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "Where'd Sayaka run off to...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"Anyway, that video was pretty convincing. I almost\n"
"thought it was real..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid "But it's fake, right? It's gotta be!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid "I'd like to believe that, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>If it *was* real...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid "I-I don't wanna talk about..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid "And I'm sure you d-don't wanna hear it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"But if y-you really insist, you need to convince\n"
"everyone e-else to talk first!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>What kind of monitor is this!? Who would even make\n"
"this kind of thing!?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"It has \"Monokuma Co.\" written across it. I guess\n"
"they've covered all the details..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>A surveillance camera...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I hate the idea that someone might be watching me\n"
"right now.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I have to keep in mind that it's against school\n"
"regulations to mess with any of the cameras.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>As much as it gets on my nerves, I'd better leave it\n"
"alone.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Huh? There's something inside this cardboard box.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It's...!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid "...a bunch of DVDs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid "And each one has a label on it with someone's name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0071"
msgid ""
"This must be the \"<CLT 3>video for each of us<CLT>\" he\n"
"mentioned..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0072"
msgid "I'd better go tell everyone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0073"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She just ran off...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0074"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I didn't follow after her. I just stood right there\n"
"where I was.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0075"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The DVDs in front of me had robbed me of all\n"
"awareness. I was rooted in place...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0076"
msgid "I think I see something..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0077"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It's the cardboard box the DVDs were in.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0078"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Next to the monitor is a high-end DVD player. It\n"
"should be able to play DVDs.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0079"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But I don't see any actual discs nearby...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0080"
msgid ""
"A DVD player is useless by itself. If we had something\n"
"to watch, at least that'd help pass the time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0081"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Next to the monitor is a high-end DVD player. It'll\n"
"probably play those DVDs no problem.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0082"
msgid ""
"Maybe I'll just watch mine real quick, before everyone\n"
"else gets here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0083"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I sorted through the DVDs I'd found in the box and\n"
"found the one with my name on it...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0084"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...then I slid it into the expensive-looking player.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0085"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I sat down and stared intently at the\n"
"darkened screen. And then...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0086"
msgid "Ah—!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0087"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I yelled out without realizing it, and my heart\n"
"started racing.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0088"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Because what I saw on that monitor...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0089"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It was my family.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0090"
msgid ""
"You getting picked to attend Hope's Peak Academy is\n"
"like a dream come true. Make sure you do your best!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0091"
msgid ""
"I'm so proud of you, son. But remember—don't push\n"
"yourself too hard!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0092"
msgid "Are you really watching this, Makoto? Good luck, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0093"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>If it had ended there, that would've been fine. A\n"
"message of love and support.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0094"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>After leaving my family behind to attend Hope's Peak,\n"
"it would have given me hope, given me strength.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0095"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>If this was a normal school, I would've been happy, if\n"
"a little embarrassed.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0096"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>With my family's support to rely on, I would've been\n"
"motivated to do even better.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0097"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But here, now, it was totally different.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0098"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I *wasn't* living an ordinary school life.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0099"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>So I had a pretty strong feeling that the video wasn't\n"
"going to end there.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0100"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I hated having that feeling, but...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0101"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...it turned out I was absolutely right.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0102"
msgid "...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0103"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>This time, I couldn't even make a sound.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0104"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>My voice just...died.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0105"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Where'd everyone go...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0106"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It looks like a warzone or something...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0107"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>As if in reply, a voice came floating out of the\n"
"speakers.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0108"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I recognized the voice, of course. It was *him*...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0109"
msgid ""
"Makoto Naegi, accepted into Hope's Peak Academy. And\n"
"his family, who supported such a lucky boy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0110"
msgid ""
"But it seems like...something's happened to this\n"
"family's well-being!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0111"
msgid ""
"Oh boy, this is bad! What could have possibly happened\n"
"to this family's well-being!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0112"
msgid "Wh-What is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0113"
msgid "What happened to everyone!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0114"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I started trembling...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0115"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I could feel the fear and anger building up inside me,\n"
"like hot magma.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0116"
msgid "GOD DAMMIT!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0117"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I slammed my fist against the desk over and over\n"
"again. A single thought was racing through my mind...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0118"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>What else? How could I think about anything else?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0119"
msgid "I have to get out of here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0120"
msgid ""
"I have to get out, right now! I need to make sure\n"
"everyone's safe!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0121"
msgid "Makoto...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0122"
msgid "What happened? Make sure who's safe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0123"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I noticed everyone standing around the entrance to the\n"
"A/V room. They stared at me, faces full of confusion.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0124"
msgid "Wh-What's going on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0125"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Without a word, I pointed to the cardboard box.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0126"
msgid "Is that what Monokuma was talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0127"
msgid "What's on them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0128"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>They all gathered around the box, and each of them\n"
"grabbed the DVD with their name on it.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0129"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>One by one, they each rushed to a monitor.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0130"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It didn't take long for them to react.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0131"
msgid "What the fuck...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0132"
msgid ""
"Th-This can't be real, right? It has to be fake,\n"
"right!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0133"
msgid "Yeah, no way it's real. Haha...no way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0134"
msgid "I can't t-take it anymore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0135"
msgid "I c-can't take this anymore! Let me out of h-here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0136"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>As soon as I saw their reactions, I knew... They'd all\n"
"seen something like what I'd seen.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0137"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Nobody even bothered trying to hide their fear and\n"
"confusion.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0138"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Except for *her*. Even now, she was totally calm.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0139"
msgid "I see... So this is what he meant by <CLT 3>motive<CLT>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0140"
msgid ""
"He wants to fuel our <CLT 3>desire to leave<CLT> so that we're\n"
"more likely to start killing each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0141"
msgid "It is the classic \"prisoner's dilemma.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0142"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0143"
msgid ""
"Let me use an example. Imagine two countries are on\n"
"the brink of war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0144"
msgid ""
"But both countries want peace, and each commits to\n"
"scaling back their forces as a sign of good faith."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0145"
msgid ""
"But there's a chance that one country may betray the\n"
"other, so each country fears lowering their guard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0146"
msgid ""
"The result is that neither scales back their forces,\n"
"and they both end up betraying each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0147"
msgid ""
"In other words, the fear of invisible treachery\n"
"becomes the greatest enemy of stability."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0148"
msgid "That kinda sounds l-like us right now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0149"
msgid ""
"Everyone says they'll work together, but in our hearts\n"
"we're all afraid someone might betray us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0150"
msgid ""
"Don't put those awful thoughts in our head! That's\n"
"exactly what they *want* us to do!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0151"
msgid ""
"You can say that, but maybe you're thinking that once\n"
"everyone drops their guard, you can just..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0152"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0153"
msgid ""
"This is exactly what Monokuma, or whoever's behind\n"
"this, wants. They *want* us to fight. Don't you see?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0154"
msgid "Yeah, you're right. We all need to calm down..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0155"
msgid ""
"Okay, then. Maybe we should start by all\n"
"just...talking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0156"
msgid ""
"Maybe if we all just talk about what we saw, that'll\n"
"help get everything out of our system."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0157"
msgid "Besides, I think we're all super curious, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0158"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I wonder what was in everyone's videos...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0159"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I'd be lying if I said I wasn't curious.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0160"
msgid "Hey, Sayaka..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0161"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0162"
msgid "What was in your video, Sayaka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0163"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0164"
msgid "What's wr-wrong? Just hurry up and t-tell us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0165"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0166"
msgid "Sayaka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0167"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I gently placed my hand on her shoulder.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0168"
msgid "...Stop it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0169"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She pushed my hand away and suddenly ran off.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0170"
msgid "Sayaka!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0171"
msgid "Let her go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0172"
msgid "I-I can't do that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0173"
msgid "I have to go make sure she's okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0174"
msgid ""
"I h-hate romantic comedies like this. I don't care\n"
"what h-happens to her, personally..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0175"
msgid "That's because you're totally thoughtless!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0176"
msgid "I'm...really worried."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0177"
msgid ""
"Then why don't you go do whatever you think you have\n"
"to? We don't all have to stick around together, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0178"
msgid ""
"Speaking of which, I have my own things to take care\n"
"of. Goodbye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0179"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Everyone went their separate ways...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0180"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But I don't have time to worry about them right now.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0181"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I have to go find Sayaka!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0182"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0183"
msgid "We should probably look around a little bit more."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0184"
msgid "This is where we can play the videos, I think."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0185"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I need to find out what's on the DVD.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0186"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I wonder what's in these videos...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0187"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0188"
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0189"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Leave the area?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
